OL,3,CMerseyside families offered help and
OL,4,Csupport by bereavement charity
OL,6,FA bereavement charity that supports
OL,7,Ffamilies through the loss of a child
OL,8,Fis extending its services across
OL,9,FMerseyside.
OL,11,F2wish was founded in 2012 by Rhian
OL,12,FMannings, following the tragic loss of
OL,13,Fher baby son George who had just
OL,14,Fcelebrated his first birthday.
OL,16,FFive days after George's death,
OL,17,FRhian's husband Paul also took his own
OL,18,Flife, consumed by grief.
