OL,3,CMerseyside families offered help and
OL,4,Csupport by bereavement charity
OL,6,FWith no support available at that
OL,7,Ftime, Rhian was left to navigate the
OL,8,Fdevastation alone with her two young
OL,9,Fchildren.
OL,11,FRhian said:
OL,13,F"When my son died we had nothing
OL,14,Fwhatsoever and I had three young
OL,15,Fchildren, I had support from health
OL,16,Fvisitors and midwives but then when
OL,17,Fone of your children dies unexpectedly
OL,18,Fthere's nothing, most people expect
OL,19,Fthere is something there. There are
OL,20,Freally great pockets of work but not
OL,21,Fevery family will get that support"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
