OL,3,CMerseyside families offered help and
OL,4,Csupport by bereavement charity
OL,6,F"They'll get a call from us and then
OL,7,Freally we are led by the family as
OL,8,Fevery family is very different but we
OL,9,Fwill offer to go out to their home as
OL,10,Fsoon as possible, just to sit with
OL,11,Fthem and talk to them, have a cup of
OL,12,Ftea and then we have a variety of
OL,13,Fdifferent services, counselling,
OL,14,Fcomplimentary therapy and group
OL,15,Fsupport."
OL,17,FThe expansion of the charity into
OL,18,FMerseyside is part of its growth into
OL,19,Fthe North West with teams already
OL,20,Fworking Cheshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
