OL,6,FPrince William has recently met up
OL,7,Fwith Rhian to discuss the charity and
OL,8,Fit's work to mark World mental health
OL,9,Fday
OL,11,FIt's the second time the Prince has
OL,12,Fmet with Rhian and as he visited her
OL,13,Fhome in Cardiff he became visibly
OL,14,Fupset as they discussed her loss.
